Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here, Code: Breaker.\NWhat happened to Heike?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I kicked that traitor's ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But never mind him, you're\Nsure looking good, Prime Minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so unkind of you, Toki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.33,0:00:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you know, please\Ncome and untie these ropes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not as though I'm\Nhere because I want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I were to choose\Nthe option of forsaking you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:37.89,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Remaining time until Prime Minister\NFujiwara's public execution"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:07.58,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is there no final{\i}\N{\i1}piece to unravel this puzzle?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:14.88,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wander around the search area with dread{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:22.39,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With shaky self-confidence{\i}\N{\i1}facing unyielding damnation,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:26.23,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm still alive, but I can't catch up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:32.44,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to residual images of hidden memories{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:36.61,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let loose dark shame unbounded{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:40.45,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to the ends of this world of kindness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:44.54,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even hopes best forgotten are silenced{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:48.21,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as corruption spreads out before our eyes{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:51.42,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Consign it to darkness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:55.13,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An ego on trial{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:02:06.35,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a moment of hesitation is seen ecstasy{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you have\Nthe children with special abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to let these children\Nlive their whole lives in a cage?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Your former leader, Hitomi,\Nwants to avoid having them do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For me to leave here together with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,would mean being pursued\Nfor the rest of my life! As a criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi said that if it meant\Nbeing kept as a dog of the state,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,they would be better off\Nsurviving out in the wilderness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't become dogs!\NWe will not let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you're forsaking Hitomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just with Hitomi\Nunder a temporary contract!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll save the children\Nwith special abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll save Hitomi, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not going to forsake anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:07.04,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\be6\an8}"Episode 12: 'Devils... God\Nand Man... Sakura Watching Over'"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying so hard, Ogami?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the bombs, Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.\NIt doesn't matter what I want,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,they detonate when their time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way they are set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's watch on together for\Nthe moment when the world changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment when\Nthe people are terrorized,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and yearn for those\Nof us with special abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no longer any need\Nfor anyone to face death in solitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A world where we can live\Nout under the sun is on its way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that, Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:04:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My, what an adorable little renegade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Puppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami, you have a seat and watch, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You still want to go at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you getting up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, there's\Nno stopping the bombs now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Bombs? Sending all\Nthose people to their deaths?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you?! Is that\NCode: Breaker, Code 01, Hitomi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the Hitomi I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Code: Breaker, huh?\NWhat nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami, you've realized, haven't you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that all of the killing that Eden orders
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,ends up serving to give the state\Nand Eden the upper hand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That bunch of gangsters that you burned up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,they were only targeted\Nbecause they were helping me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many other\Ngroups of gangsters out there
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,who do terrible things, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The same with Tabata.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He was killed because he\Nwas providing me with information.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The same is true of G-Falcon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They were chosen to be an\Nexample to warn off other gangsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Eden ignores all sorts of evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and only chooses to label as evil\Nthose who are inconvenient to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They then use Code: Breakers\Nto do their killing for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,so they can keep their hands clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you take pride in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In being Code: Breakers,\Nwho are kept by Eden?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Live for all you're worth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he is a Devilfiend,\Nhe's still my papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Fireballman, you dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Come after me to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisa, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's fight together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's fight together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami, let's bring justice to a world
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of those with special abilities, together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...together...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it. Eden is evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hitomi, you're also killing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and assigning reasons\Nthat are convenient to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You have killed innocent people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You declared that\Nthey're unworthy of protection,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and then killed many of those\Npeople to achieve your own goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You are evil. And I am also\Nan evil, who has killed much evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're both evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,then I will fight until my last\Nmoment to protect those people!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I would want to be someone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,who would save others\Nuntil the very last moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not fight together with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a Code: Breaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad, Ogami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,At least let me be\Nthe one to send you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't do any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Ogami?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you use your flames anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gone Lost, huh, Ogami?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Lost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt, Ogami?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain of those with\Nspecial abilities... Our destiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, Eden doesn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait, Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you kill Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a good girl.\NYou were raised by good parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, is that really where the guys
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,who are sending\Nout the bomb signals are?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The bombs are where\Nthey're marked on the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What are children doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we really do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi said not to get involved with anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is for the sake of\Neveryone with special abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?\NIt's dangerous here, so why don't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They have the same kind of\Npowers as Ogami and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do this anymore, Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to defend Ogami by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Sakurakoji...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think your straightforward\Nfeelings are fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes more than\Nthat to change the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you interfere, I'll show no mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Special abilities don't work\Non you, so I'll have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have the strength\Nright now to save this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment of the blast is getting near.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and\Nsave me, Code: Breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you planning on watching me die?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait until after the Prime Minister's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.09,0:10:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as the slaughter\Nof the other 50,000,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,before I kill this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've watched a lot\Nof Code: Breakers die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You will experience it, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the sense of helplessness you\Nget from being unable to protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi... Don't... Don't...\Nblow them up... This isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, an age when those of\Nus with special abilities
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,can live out under\Nthe sun is about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We can escape our destiny to die\Nwithout anyone knowing who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Our days of solitude are ending!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It was stopped, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I took some measures of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Heike?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over, Number two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Under my direction,\NI had Yuki go to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't have the children\Nwith special abilities, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The explosions aren't happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Has the mission failed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Under Heike's instructions,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,we had the children\Nmoved to another location.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you were buying time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I pretended to have\Nbeen killed to fool Hitomi,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and put a halt to his plans.\NHeike headed up the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, snow boy.\NAre you still around?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch yourself, Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so it was you after all, Heike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew the reasons\Nwhy I set up this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:13:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It was to save those\Nof us with special abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It is over, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Heike!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace! If you use that much of\Nyour special ability, you'll go Lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't use up too much power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There are still some\Nthings I need to have you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I... am not going Lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you've won, Heike?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot make the bombs across\Nthe country detonate any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki is rescuing the Prime Minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Your plans have been ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you if you thought you've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think I chose\NSky Tower as the final location?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you'd caught wind of where I was,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,there's still one last measure in place,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to ensure that my plan does not fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Using my special ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I will emit my electrical waves from Sky Tower,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and detonate all of\Nthe bombs across the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my final battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not do it, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to have\Navoided using this means,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,if at all possible, Heike.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean... you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Scared you good,\Nthere, huh, Prime Minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave me quite a start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it looks like you\Nmanaged to prevent the blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, good work.\NNow, hurry and untie me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:15:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, his fate is in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If I kill him, Sissy will be set free.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for?\NHurry up and untie my ropes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki, what are you trying to pull?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I busted the camera.\NThe only one watching right now is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No one will know the truth\Nabout what happens to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop, Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I-If I fall, I'll die! Stop it, Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Toki! Whoa... whoa...\NI'm going to fall! I'm going to fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to you panic! How disgraceful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Every once in a while, you need\Nto be put in your place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Toki? Do you feel relieved now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I should get an award\Nfor that performance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you had your chance,\Nand you didn't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a kept dog after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,While you may have been able
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to take advantage of\Nthe bombing to forsake me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you were too scared to do it yourself, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I should have used\NNenene as the Code: Breaker, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you despicable father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going shopping with Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that will do. Unless you\Nwant to make Nenene into a killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you will obey me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That was our agreement, wasn't it,\NCode: Breaker, Code 04, Toki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The fun is just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Back the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Something else you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can kill you at any time.\NBut I'm not going to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph, you don't have the guts to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to keep me from becoming like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:16:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let being a Code: Breaker...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't use it for my own desires,\Nand become the same as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot do this, Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,With this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oji! Then you're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And Yuki! Blasting me up here,\Nbike and all?! You're crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What choice was there? It was\Nthe only way to get here in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi, we won't let you go any farther.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you interfere with me,\Nthen I'll take you out first!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Number five!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off already, Number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why have you changed so much?!\NWhere did the old Number one go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not anyone who\Nwould do something like this! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?!\NTell us, Number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand anything, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Working together, as friends\Nhelping each other was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I miss those days.\NOnce, I was inside that circle, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But as long as Eden is in\Ncharge of the Code: Breakers,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and everyone else with special abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,our fate to die like dogs as\Ntheir pawns will never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Eden is just using our feelings\Nof sympathy toward our friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you see that your\Nactions are slamming the door
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,on the future of those\Nof us with special abilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we are, there's no way\Nyou can drag innocent people into this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The people who I once\Nfought to protect are culpable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They do not know that we have\Nbeen risking our lives for their peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't know how many\NCode: Breakers have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They just enjoy their peace in ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They keep on living their\Nlives of peace and security!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:20:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't even realize\Nthat they're being protected!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If that isn't a crime, then what is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late now! From the day\Nthat Eden started chasing me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the world has changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi! I have been\Nwatching how you fought!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How you've protected so many people!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember how you helped them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No you don't. That's something\Nyou don't get to do, Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not something you get to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not do it! Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You interfere, right up to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it means eradicating\Nthe people of this country
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,who have indulged themselves in peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I will liberate those\Nwho have special abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,An eye for an eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A tooth for a tooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Evil for evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've... changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.39,0:21:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're steeped entirely in evil.\NI'm gonna burn you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Outstanding! Such... power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:22:01.34,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, you, too, will know{\i}\N{\i1}where that white crow is heading{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:07.01,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We fly through the brilliant city,{\i}\N{\i1}unnoticed by all around{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:21.52,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looking only for a reason to live{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:26.95,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ashamed of our hollow selves{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:31.70,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should we just laugh and go along{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:37.33,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with the rules the world has decided on?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.33,0:22:42.04,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stripped bare, following{\i}\N{\i1}wherever our instincts lead{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:46.13,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to the truth from{\i}\N{\i1}which we've averted our eyes{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.13,0:22:50.76,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Verdicts handed down for no one's sake{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.76,0:22:55.60,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cast off the dark robes and get on your feet{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:23:00.44,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pure white wishes become our wings{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.44,0:23:05.11,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shake off your hesitations now, and fly high{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.11,0:23:13.53,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have no fear; the answers{\i}\N{\i1}lie beyond the darkness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki... Yuki... Oji... Heike... Hitomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, "Code: Breaker" episode 13,\N"A Flower Blooming With God."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Ogami.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.43,0:23:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Ogami.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Ogami.
